                </svg>
                <h2 class="fw-normal">Malta</h2>
                <p>Book you appointment for every Malta VISA.</p>
                <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href=""@Url.Action("about", "Home")"">Send details &raquo;</a></p>
            </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        </div><!-- /.row -->



        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <h2 class="featurette-heading fw-normal lh-1">Send us your detail.<br> <span class="text-body-secondary">Book appointment easily and swiftly.</span></h2>
                <p class="lead">We can book appointment for any country around the world</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <svg class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" width="500" height="500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder: 500x500" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
                    <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="var(--bs-secondary-bg)" />
                    <image href="~/Images/b_a.gif" width="100%" height="100%" />
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette">
            <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
                <h2 class="featurette-heading fw-normal lh-1">Oh yeah, it’s that good. <span class="text-body-secondary">See for yourself.</span></h2>
                <p class="lead">You can als apply for student VISA and also for Working VISA and also for Family Reunification and also for Short term VISA.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
                <svg class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" width="500" height="500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder: 500x500" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
                    <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="var(--bs-secondary-bg)" />
                    <image href="~/Images/WorldMap.png" width="100%" height="100%" />
                </svg>
